WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Welcome to the giant wheel, a breathtaking ride above the city.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:09.000
As we ascend, you'll see a stunning panoramic view all around.

00:00:09.500 --> 00:00:14.000
This Ferris wheel stands 150 meters tall and has 40 cabins.

00:00:14.500 --> 00:00:19.000
Each cabin can hold up to 8 people, making it perfect for families.

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:24.000
The ride lasts around 15 minutes, offering a smooth experience.

00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:29.000
Don't forget to take pictures as we reach the highest point of the ride.

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:30.000
Enjoy your ride!
